{"tid":1461112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭 你知唔知我哋最後目的係咩呀？","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T06:25:33.000Z","uid":293341,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9742c1c2278c3456876b855718add3b5f8ebc502","tid":1461112,"uid":293341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>If we burn, you burn with us. </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果訴求得唔到回應，我哋係打算攬炒。<br />\n我哋唔怕你嘅抹黑，你抹得愈黑，對我哋愈有利。<br />\n你喺記者會提到經濟差、社會亂、分化市民、挑撥情緒，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢啲正正就係我哋想睇到嘅結果</span></span>。多謝你幫手製造社會恐慌，多謝你幫手話比市民知示威嘅力量係可以幾咁龐大，多謝你令市民發聲，多謝你令所有牛鬼蛇神浮面，讓香港人睇清一切皮肉下嘅真心同獸心。<br />\n<br />\n其實你應該好撚驚攬炒，因為攬炒最大損失就係政治家、商家、上流社會。多謝你，一手摧毀佢哋用剝削嘅手段而得返嚟嘅「收成期」。"},{"pid":"144b7fb95ee20679f90f52fc604f43c798311508","tid":1461112,"uid":100714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />u burn with us"},{"pid":"550e731906d3574a378dccfba42791ae7cadf217","tid":1461112,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:25:02.000Z","msg":"對付林鄭，要草船借箭<br />\n催淚彈已經係常餐，會唔會有手足去禮賓府開餐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"36b6bf4e76d8522913f04efecdb461ca795e5693","tid":1461112,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:25:33.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你要我死<br />\n我要你收皮"}]}